name: AI Avatar #158 (Princess of the Night)
description:
“Her long and flowing silvery hair shimmers with tints of blue, both being the colors of her royal lineage. The stars seem to follow her wherever she goes, gently illuminating her delicate face and eyes. Like a servant, the darkness too parts and gives way to its liege … the Princess of the Night.”

---

This Avatar was created using an AI (Generative Adversarial Network) over countless iterations, with the goal of achieving the Pinnacle of Human Beauty. Just as each Human is unique, each Avatar is Forever Unique. Each Avatar will only be minted once and there will be no copies.
